item.description:
@davidi2 wrote:

0:40, says the username of the person you are luring is Pac Man. Quick highscore lookup told me that person is not ranked, which is impossible for a 102+12.

I also looked at the minimap and wilderness level and compared it to the Wilderness map, and it didn’t match up. I’m calling bullshit.

Either way this is just stupid channel promotion to try and get subscribers, so I’m locking this.

You wouldn’t know though because you’re the manipulater.

No he took the method from some kid who RWTs and gets banned for it then denies it. Although we can’t tell actually who it is since he blurs out everything in the video leading me to believe its not him actually but just a private server or a stolen video.[/quote]

because i dont want you people finding my RS name? for simple reasons like

  1. i’d be harassed, hated and probally flamed
  2. so i wont be famous enough to get banned for “RWT” which innocent people are being banned for it.
  3. i want my luring career to keep going not be famous for doing it and everyone is like " stay away from him he will lure you !"
